Package sudoku.cs.event

Interface Summary
GameStatusChangedListener Listener for game status change events.
PlayerChangedListener Listener for player change events.
PuzzleChangedListener Listener for puzzle change events.
 

Class Summary
GameStatusChangedEvent Encapsulates the event that the game's status has changed.
PlayerChangedEvent Tells the lister that the Player list has changed.
PuzzleChangedEvent An event that is shared with the client so that the puzzle can be updated when it is changed.
 

Enum Summary
State Enumeration of Client (game) states.
